[[Chiyero chekupimisa]] (Unit of measure) zvinoreva mwero une huwandu hwakatarwa pamitemo yenyika kana Pasirose, kuti uve [[chidzikwe]] (standard) chinoshandiswa pakupima mhando yehuwandu ihwohwo. 

Somuenzaniso kana tichipima nhambwe tinoshandisa chiyero chinonzi mita (metre).

Pasirose sangano re International Organisation for Standardization ndiro rine [[hutongi]] hwekutara '''zvidzikwe''' zvinoshandiswa pakupima mipimo yakasiyana-siyana.

